He who observes the situation is wise, and he who controls the situation wins.
Under the external environment of the in-depth development of economic globalization, the market and resources have played an important role in China's rapid development.
Now, the world under the impact of the epidemic is undergoing profound changes, facing more unstable and uncertain factors, and economic globalization is facing headwinds and turning back waves.
One of the most important aspects of making good ideological and work preparations for coping with changes in the external environment for a long time and promoting China's economy to ride the wind and waves and achieve stability and far-reaching, is to take expanding and meeting domestic demand as the strategic basis for development, give full play to its own advantages, and add impetus to China's economic development and promote the recovery of the world economy by prospering the domestic economy and smoothing the domestic circulation.
