The vascular surgery of Shanghai Changhai Hospital is the only institute of vascular surgery in the whole army and the only clinical medical center of vascular system diseases in Shanghai. It is also the first national key discipline of vascular surgery. It is the top team with profound accumulation in the industry.
Professor Huang Xiaojin, Director of Vascular Surgery, Zhongshan Hospital Affiliated to Xiamen University, was interviewed by the media.
Vascular Surgery of Zhongshan Hospital affiliated to Xiamen University is the first independent discipline of vascular surgery in Fujian Province. It has been dedicated to the diagnosis and treatment of aortic and peripheral vascular diseases for a long time, and was approved to build a provincial key clinical specialty in 2018.
In the treatment of aortic diseases, besides dissecting aneurysm and aortic aneurysm, he has rich experience in emergency ruptured aortic aneurysm.
"The vascular surgery of Zhongshan Hospital affiliated to Xiamen University is outstanding in the region from the development history, the breadth, difficulty and complexity of the operation. Therefore, this time we set up a collaboration center, which can also be used in the diagnosis and treatment of lower limb arteries and carotid arteries. Carry out all-round in-depth cooperation in medicine, teaching and scientific research."
Professor Rui Feng, deputy director of vascular surgery at Shanghai Changhai Hospital, said.
In 2018, Zhongshan Hospital affiliated to Xiamen University and Shanghai Changhai Hospital signed a contract to establish Li Zhaoshen's Famous Doctor Studio in Department of Gastroenterology.
Professor Huang Xiaojin, director of vascular surgery in our hospital, said in an interview with Zhongxin.com that the vascular surgery in our hospital also has a long history of exchanges with Changhai Hospital. The two hospitals formally formed a cooperative unit, which brought the cooperation and exchanges between the two sides to a new level.
